creator: phuocly
descriptionHtml:
Clash of Maps 2023:COC Layouts app helps you get the best layout link for your village. Copy the base in one click! Share the clash of clans base designs with your friends to help them grind too. Share the clash of clans base layout with the clan mates to help them in war, get trophy, coins & elixir.

How can this app help me?
This app can help you get the best base for your village like war base, farm base, troll base, CWL, Hybrid base, legend league base, ring base etc.

Features of Clash of Maps app:

- Thounsand of bases.
- Town hall maps from 3 to 15 (TH5, Th6, Th7, Th8, Th9, Th10, Th11, Th12, Th13, TH14, TH15).
- Builder Hall layouts from 4 to 9 (Bh4, Bh5, Bh6, Bh7, Bh8, Bh9).
- Save the base with copy link in your favorites list.
- Every base comes with copy link.
- We updates new bases every day or so.
- You will get a notification when new bases are available.
- Unique bases.
- Trusted by pro
